name: GreenThumb
0:
”Alexa, ask green thumb to set watering time.”
”Alexa, ask green thumb to get watering time.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: green thumb
des: Tired of not knowing when the plants were watered? Or maybe the plants get watered too much? This skill can help! Whenever the plants get watered just let the skill know! It will remember the time and if someone else wants to water the plants they can check the skill first!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
